      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<size=150%><b>SQL Injection</b></size>


    1. <color=#569CD6><b>Action:</b></color>
    Replace your standard <color=#DCDCAA>Statement</color> with a <color=#4EC9B0>PreparedStatement</color>
    and use <color=#CE9178>"?"</color> placeholders instead of adding variables directly
    to the string.



    2. <color=#569CD6><b>Logic:</b></color> By sending the
    <color=#CE9178>SQL structure</color> first, the database "locks in" the command.
    When data is sent later via <color=#DCDCAA>setString</color>, it is treated strictly
    as a <color=#CE9178>Literal Value</color>, making it impossible for a hacker
    to "inject" new commands.'
