      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<size=150%><b>Broken Access Control</b></size>



    1. <color=#569CD6><b>Action:</b></color>
    Insert the <color=#DCDCAA>requireRole</color>(<color=#CE9178>"admin"</color>)
    function into your route. This acts as a <color=#4EC9B0>security gate</color>
    that blocks unauthorized access.



    2. <color=#569CD6><b>Logic:</b></color>
    While <color=#DCDCAA>authenticate</color> checks **who** you are, <color=#DCDCAA>requireRole</color>
    checks **what** you are allowed to do. This ensures only users with the <color=#CE9178>"admin"</color>
    tag can enter.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
